Package: gglaplot
Title: Makes graphics in the GLA style using ggplot2
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Libby", "Rogers", email = "Libby.Rogers@london.gov.uk",
                    role = c("aut","cre")),
             person("Mike", "Brondbjerg", email = "Mike.Brondbjerg@london.gov.uk",
                    role = c("aut", "art")),
             person("Marta", "Lapsley", email = "Marta.Lapsley@london.gov.uk",
                    role = "ctb"))
Description: The package provides several wrappers and tools to use with ggplot2
             to make graphics that follow the GLA City Intelligence Data Design Guidelines.
